snippet.title: Confused Bi-Product of a Misinformed Culture
snippet.description:
I was listening to some music the other day when I finally understood why it is that I do what I do here. When a song hits, I don't care if anyone else likes it. It's the only thing I know of where no one else's opinion matters but my own. I think it's important to be able to enjoy something that stands alone in this mad world of ours. What I do here, these mixes... They are my attempt at creating that space of personal power where we can all stand apart fromt the madness of the world and embrace the freedom found within. 

"One good thing about music, when it hits you, you feel no pain"
-Bob Marley
